data.description: Step into an airy atmosphere filled with various desirable finishes, and ample living space. Nestled in a lovely neighborhood less than 15 minutes from the center of San Antonio and just minutes from South Park Mall, Lackland AFB, Harlandale Park, Texas Vista Medical Center, and multiple dining, shopping and entertainment options. Look forward to saving on future electric bills with the help of the equipped solar panels! Six bedrooms, two studies, a comfortable living and dining room and some great storage areas, ensure plenty of space to suit everyone's needs. The interesting layout provides the possibility of multiple uses. The huge backyard is ready for some outdoor fun! This property is ready for new homeowners to fall in love with. Click the Virtual Tour link to view the 3D Tour.
